==Useful Info==
'''Gnoll bouda''' are support casters often found with packs of standard [[Gnoll (monster)|gnoll]]s. Only slightly more physically powerful than a regular gnoll, they aren't much of a threat alone, but can speed up and heal their allies while weakening you.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Weakening gaze severely and irresistibly neuters your damage output for a short duration. Try to not let them get into line of sight until you want to actually fight them.
*Try to lure them away from their group. That way they can't heal their fellow gnolls or speed their movement up.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.29]], gnoll bouda were known as '''gnoll shamans'''. Also, they lost [[Haste Other]] for Hunting Call and [[Corona]] for Weakening Gaze.
*Prior to [[0.14]], gnoll shamans knew [[Petrify]].
